author: Caitlin Huey-Burns
title: Stay-at-home candidate: Biden competes with White House for message
description: From his basement, Biden tries to counter the White House on COVID-19.
content: Just weeks ago, Joe Biden was riding high on stunning primary wins, starting to fill rallies with thousands, dominating headlines, and quickly coalescing the Democratic Party around his candidacy. Now he is hunkered down in his Wilmington basement, forced to … [+5991 chars]
